The overarching ambitions driving these developments are, predictably, rather grand and occasionally alarming. They include, but are not limited to, the pursuit of [Artificial general intelligence](/Artificial_general_intelligence)—that elusive, sentient digital being that will either save us or condemn us—the creation of sophisticated [Intelligent agent](/Intelligent_agent)s, and the somewhat terrifying prospect of [Recursive self-improvement](/Recursive_self-improvement) where AI perpetually enhances itself, presumably beyond human comprehension. More tangible, immediate goals involve advancements in areas such as [Planning](/Automated_planning_and_scheduling), [Computer vision](/Computer_vision), mastering [General game playing](/General_game_playing), refining [Knowledge representation](/Knowledge_representation_and_reasoning), perfecting [Natural language processing](/Natural_language_processing), and the practical application of [Robotics](/Robotics). And, naturally, there's the ever-present, often-ignored concern of [AI safety](/AI_safety), a topic frequently discussed in hushed tones after the fact.

